            </h1>
            <p className="text-base sm:text-xl text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed tracking-tight px-4">
                Evaluation for the <span className="text-[#8A6E99]">9-Unit Residential Complex</span>. Comparing <span className="text-[#8A6E99]">STR</span>, <span className="text-[#D4AF37]">STR</span> & <span className="text-[#2A5B64]">LTR Models</span>.
